{"tid":259901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又係.. 用影印機印大奶 搞到入醫院","createTime":"2017-05-27T10:05:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-28T03:06:37.000Z","uid":72009,"like":121,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1bda9c32a6f05dd23135ce2628350c72201c0519","tid":259901,"uid":72009,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T10:05:40.000Z","msg":"新加坡一個妙齡女在朋友慫恿之下，全裸在超商內印奶，結果胸部燙傷送醫。《TELEGRAPH SUN》報導，新加坡25歲女子日前與朋友打賭，要她全裸在超商影印機印奶，她不甘示弱果真脫光，沒想到機器高熱傷了她雙乳皮膚。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n她的朋友受訪均表示後悔，原以為是無傷大雅的玩笑竟然釀禍，「如果我們知道她會受傷，絕對不會要她打這個賭」。超商男店員則說，她見到一個裸女跑進店裡，直接衝過櫃台跑到影印機前面，他不敢上前阻止，只好遠遠觀察，「我叫她不要按，但她還是按了影印鍵」。女子按下按鍵後，一道光劃過她的胸部，她發出尖叫聲隨後開始咒罵，男店員趕緊上前幫忙，看到她胸部被燒紅，男店員立刻從冰櫃中拿出冰水潑灑她的胸部。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170527/640_b3980f6ae3dc6263e388f784248384f8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170527%2F640_b3980f6ae3dc6263e388f784248384f8.jpg&h=47e164a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />新加坡今天追好多分"},{"pid":"0b4efc20ee7031af49f9293d7b0d76d1e2a981d1","tid":259901,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T10:11:49.000Z","msg":"點解會熱?"},{"pid":"503e9dfed971452f7e4e1ab814a074b7dfde3d25","tid":259901,"uid":93900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T10:13:19.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"81208c24c084e375ccf92c633637806e5a94a7a7","tid":259901,"uid":88117,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T10:16:12.000Z","msg":"個店員應該射篤精幫佢降温"},{"pid":"de5617db8d4dded1315e98214623c4312394f061","tid":259901,"uid":116402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T10:19:06.000Z","msg":"開始拍得住神洲"},{"pid":"3837a5e134a9b9a6b07f81aacc82dc7eabb4c70e","tid":259901,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T10:20:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji